      "description": "Thinly slice the apples and red chilli."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Grate your Parmesan then blend it with the juice of half a lemon, jalapeño, avocado and Dijon mustard until smooth. Season with salt and pepper."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Cook the bulgur wheat according to packet instructions."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Pile the bulgur wheat into a bowl and top with the crispy kale, chickpeas, apples and drizzle with the avocado dressing. Top with sliced chillies and enjoy."
